Explain the key ideas in Key Takeaway, distinguish evidence from assumption, and apply them to a practical digital-asset decision.

### Key Takeaway

Market structure reveals which side currently has control.

Higher highs and higher lows favour buyers. Lower highs and lower lows favour sellers. A range shows temporary balance.

Do not attempt to predict every turning point.

Identify the structure, define the level that must hold and change your view when the market—not your emotions—provides evidence that control has shifted.','markdown',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,0,0,'','',6,1785297600000 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM `courses` WHERE `id`='cognizen-crypto-mastery-foundations-production');
