On a DEX, the transaction is executed by code—but the responsibility for understanding and authorising it remains yours.','markdown',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,0,0,'','',9,1785297600000 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM `courses` WHERE `id`='cognizen-crypto-mastery-foundations-production');
